## Commands

```bash
# Dependencies
uv sync

# Testing
uv run pytest                    # 跑全部測試
uv run pytest -v --tb=long       # 詳細輸出（debugging 時用）

# Lint & Format
uv run ruff check .              # Lint
uv run ruff format .             # Format
uv run ruff check . --fix        # Auto-fix

# Type Check
uv run pyright
```

